description:
There are only 5 categories you need to build a balanced plant-based pantry.  You don't need a lot. I'll share those pantry basics and fridge and cupboard essentials that are must-haves so you can make delicious vegan food. Use this video as inspiration for healthy meal ideas to help you transition to a plant-based diet.

I’ll share the foods most commonly used in my home (a pantry tour of sorts) and show that you can start small and still enjoy delicious and tasty food.

