// P R O D U C T S  I  U S

Hey! This video is for you if you're considering transitioning to a plant-based vegan lifestyle! In this video, I share what I wish I knew BEFORE going plant-based vegan (a few surprises)! Though it’s one of the best decisions I’ve ever made, if I knew what to expect before I transitioned, it would've made my beginning journey a whole lot easier. I hope sharing my experience helps you transition like a boss! 

